<FIRST>u a AM-FatalCarCrashes     08-01 0376</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Fatal Car Crashes,0384</SECOND>
<HEAD>Two Accidents Kill 11, Injure 7</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
