ell </PERSON> refuses to pinpoint blame but strongly denounced the delays in replacing him. `` The disappointment to me was that for the first time in many years, the process was prolonged to the point where it was a disservice to the <ORGANIZATION> Supreme </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Court </ORGANIZATION> itself,'' he said.
